.env.sentry-build-plugin

# Next.js-generated ambient types. Regenerated on every `next` command (and by
# the `typecheck` script via `next typegen`), and its routes import flips between
# `.next/types` and `.next/dev/types` depending on whether build or dev ran last
# — tracking it just produces cross-worktree churn.
next-env.d.ts